Package: fPASS
Title: Two Sample Projection-based Test of Mean function for Functional
    Data
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Salil", "Koner", , "salil.koner@duke.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-1952-4210"))
Description: Computes the Power and Sample size required to test for the
    difference in the mean function between two groups of longitudinal data or sparsely
    observed functional data under irregular design under arbitrary covariance structure. See
    Wang (2021) <https://doi.org/10.1214/21-EJS1802> and Koner and Luo (2023) <https://arxiv.org/abs/2302.05612> for details of the testing procedure. 
